snippet.title: The Bornless Developer Vlog 1: Genesis I January 2023
snippet.description:
Join the Waitlist: 
https://tally.so/r/3xV81E

Sign up to follow the development and future early access, and join our social platforms at https://linktr.ee/TheBornless

----

Welcome to the first developer vlog for The Bornless game! We're excited to take a look back at the past year and give you a sneak peek at what's to come next.

In 2022, we've been hard at work improving the gameplay and adding new features to the game. We've received valuable feedback from our community, and we're incorporating that feedback to make the game even better.

We've also been working on creating a more immersive world, with new environments and characters to explore. We can't wait for you to see the results of our efforts.

But that's not all! In 2023, we're planning to release even more content for the game, including new levels, items, and enemies. We're also looking at ways to expand the game's story and give players even more to discover.

We're always open to hearing from our community, so if you have any feedback or suggestions, please let us know. And don't forget to stay tuned for more updates and vlogs about The Bornless game!

Thank you for your support!

---
 
About The Bornless:

Welcome to The Bornless, an action horror FPS. Face off against other players, summon demons, and build factions in a Lovecraftian world. Use Black Magick, acquire powerful weapons, upgrade your Safehouse,  and strategize to survive. 

---

The Bornless Discord: https://discord.gg/NSDs3UDVCG
The Bornless Twitter: https://twitter.com/TheBornlessGame
The Bornless TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@thebornlessgame
The Bornless Website: https://www.thebornless.com/
Cathedral Studios Website: https://www.cathedral-studios.com/
